ws: §210.12 Return of cash items and handling of returned checks. (a) *␣*␣* A paying bank that receives a cash item directly or indirectly from a Reserve Bank also may return the item prior to settlement, in accordance with §210.9(a) and its Reserve Bank's operating circular. *␣*␣* * * * * *
